<div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">Indian scholar, activist and writer (born 1952)</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">

</p>
